item.dc:creator: @OMG_its_NICK OMG its NICK
item.description:
@OMG_its_NICK wrote:

Probably when you were changing what NPC’s said, you forgot to put back or leave in some Quotation Marks "

Go check your NPChandler.java and look for what npc’s are saying and make sure they all have Quotation Marks around the text they are supposed to say.
